{panel:title=What needs to be improved?|borderColor=#ccc| titleBGColor=#faacad|bgColor=#fff}
I would like to be able to do the following at the same time
* view diff highlighting
* see the entire file the diff occurs on

This is because sometimes the lines that are shown on the diff do not show enough context and I want to see more previous or later lines to get a better idea of what is going on.

Also, I can't horizontal scroll on the view diff page. I can close the left hand menu, but what if the code is still cut off even then?
{panel}

